, "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "8fe59db", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"page-hero\"><div class=\"page-hero-bg\"><img alt=\"Elegant bride with veil at Wife To Be\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"100vw\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643216583837-f6d664d48eac?q=70&amp;w=1280&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" srcset=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643216583837-f6d664d48eac?q=70&amp;w=640&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 640w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643216583837-f6d664d48eac?q=70&amp;w=960&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 960w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643216583837-f6d664d48eac?q=70&amp;w=1280&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 1280w, https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643216583837-f6d664d48eac?q=70&amp;w=1920&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop 1920w\"/></div>\n<div class=\"container\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Our Story</span><h1>About Wife To Be</h1><div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a> \u00a0/\u00a0 About</div></div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "0d0ae6a", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "1099b9f", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"The interior of the Wife To Be bridal boutique\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1676132068623-18f6f45de4be?q=80&amp;w=900&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Two Decades, Countless Brides</span><h2>More Than Just A Bridal Shop</h2><span class=\"divider left\"></span>\n<p>Wife To Be began with a simple belief: that choosing a wedding dress should feel special from the very first hello. Over twenty years on, we still greet every bride the same way \u2014 warmly, patiently and with all the time in the world to get it right. Brides come to us from Chester, across Cheshire and further afield still, and many arrive on the recommendation of a friend, a sister or a mum we dressed years before.</p>\n<p class=\"muted\">We keep our appointments private and unhurried on purpose. When it is just you, your people and your stylist, the whole thing feels less like shopping and more like the lovely occasion it should be.</p>\n</div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "e5d2c32", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "c9e7351", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-blush\"><div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"section-head reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Why Brides Choose Us</span><h2>Elegant \u00b7 Sophisticated \u00b7 Class</h2><span class=\"divider\"></span></div>\n<div class=\"cards\">\n<article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 2 2 9l10 13L22 9 12 2z\"></path><path d=\"M2 9h20\"></path></svg> Private</span><h3>The Boutique, Just For You</h3><p class=\"muted\">Every appointment is one-to-one, so you and your guests have the space to relax and enjoy the moment.</p></div></article>\n<article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"8\" r=\"6\"></circle><path d=\"M8.21 13.89 7 22l5-3 5 3-1.21-8.12\"></path></svg> Curated</span><h3>Designers Worth The Trip</h3><p class=\"muted\">Official stockist of Sophia Tolli, Veni Infantino, Phoenix Gowns and White Rose \u2014 over 200 gowns to explore.</p></div></article>\n<article class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"card-body\"><span class=\"eyebrow\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 1 0-7.78 7.78L12 21.23l8.84-8.84a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z\"></path></svg> Expert</span><h3>Stylists Who Care</h3><p class=\"muted\">Twenty years of know-how, honest advice and a genuine love of finding each bride her perfect match.</p></div></article>\n</div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "7ce4959", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "57f87f6", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-dark\"><div class=\"container stats\">\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\" style=\"color:var(--champagne)\">20+</div><div class=\"lbl\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,.65)\">Years Experience</div></div>\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div class=\"num\" style=\"color:var(--champagne)\">200+</div><div class=\"lbl\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,.65)\">Gowns In Store</div></div>\n<div class=\"stat reveal\"><div cl